      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the Service Location Protocol Version 2's (SLPv2) use over IPv6 networks.  Since this protocol relies on UDP and TCP, the changes to support its use over IPv6 are minor. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
